                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-305-defend1647 t18260914-305-punish1727"></join>
               Confined Two Months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>COLLINS - <rs id="t18260914-305-verdict1728" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18260914-305-verdict1728" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
